snippet.title: Word problems with money and change - 3rd grade math
snippet.description:
In this lesson, we solve several different word problems that involve money and change. I emphasize mental math strategies to find the answers, but I also show how to use simple addition and subtraction (paper & pencil techniques) to solve some problems.

This lesson is meant for about 3rd grade level - the word problems are not very complicated at this level.
